3) cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech signals and their analysis. 
4) cs.SI (Signal Processing) is another possible category as the paper proposes a generative model and an inference method for analyzing speech signals. 
5) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with machine learning methods for language acquisition.
